  <description type="3">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Food security and economic cooperation are key topics for the Dutch Embassy in Uganda. The Milking the Sun program is a core initiative that the Dutch Embassy has supported since November 2014. It complements the rollout of milk cooling installations given at the organisational level (to the dairy farmer cooperatives under the UCCCU umbrella) by providing individual UCCCU members access to high quality and affordable solar products.</narrative>
